name: img_brainswipes_xcp_d-bold_T1wOnTaskBrainSwipes_bold_mean
Description: Mean QC score for functional registration (overlay of subject's T1w onto BOLD). Derived from average scores of 0 (Fail) and 1 (Pass) (or NA if QC was not performed)

name: img_brainswipes_xcp_d-bold_T1wOnTaskBrainSwipes_bold_nrev
Description: Number of reviewers for  functional registration (overlay of subject's T1w onto BOLD)

name: img_brainswipes_xcp_d-bold_T1wOnTaskBrainSwipes_bold_QC
Description: Final T1w functional registration QC score of 0 (Fail) or 1 (Pass) based on a mean QC threshold of 0.7, or NA if nrev < 10
